content:
Quickly Deploy a Retail Onboarding Journey with Industry Solutions

Increase efficiency and engage customers by using Package Manager Industry Solutions retail onboarding campaign templates with industry-specific journeys, content, automations, and landing pages.

Where: This change applies to all Marketing Cloud Engagement editions.

When: This feature is available on or after July 1, 2024.
title: Deploy Retail Onboarding Journey with Industry Solutions
